high_descs: Turn right and walk to the coffee maker on the counter.
Pick up the black mug in the coffee maker.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment and then take the mug out again.
Turn right and walk back to the coffee maker.
Place the mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Go to the right and face the where the coffee maker is.
Pick the cup up from under the coffee maker on the counter.
Go left and turn to the right to face the fridge.
Put the cup in the fridge and shut the door, then open the door and pick the cup back up and shut the door.
Go right and then turn left to face the counter where the coffee maker is.
Put the cup down under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled cup under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to the right and find the coffee machine.
Pick up the cup from the coffee machine.
Carry the cup to the left and find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the cup inside. Shut the door and then open it. Get the cup out and shut the door.
Carry the cup to the right and find the coffee machine.
Place the cup with the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and move it to the coffee machine.
